        protected void checkNullHandling(FunctionTemplate.NullHandling nullHandling)
        Description copied from class: DrillFuncHolder
        Check if function type supports provided null handling strategy.

        Keep in mind that this method is invoked in DrillFuncHolder.DrillFuncHolder(FunctionAttributes, FunctionInitializer) constructor so make sure not to use any state fields when overriding the method to avoid uninitialized state.
